quote:
Change your thoughts
and
you change your world.

Three things in life
your health
your mission
and the people you love.
That’s it.

Those who realize their folly
 are not true fools.

Keep your eyes on the stars
and your feet on the ground.

It’s better 
to be a lion for a day
than a sheep all your life.

Life is a question 
and how we live it
 is our answer.

Keep looking up…
that’s the secret of life.

It always seems impossible
until it’s done.

Life is too important
to be taken seriously.

Life is 
like a box of chocolates.
You never know 
what you’re going to get.
Life isn’t a matter of milestones  but of moments.

Not how long, but how well
you have lived is the main thing.

I love those who
 can smile in trouble.

Be happy
for this moment.
This moment is your life.

Life is what happens
when you’re busy
making other plans.

Very little is needed
 to make a happy life.

You’ve gotta dance
like there’s nobody watching.

Believe 
that life is worth living
 and your belief will help
 create the fact.

Don't take life
too seriously.
You will never get out of it alive.

Don’t search
for the meaning of life.
Simply be present
for the people you love.

The trick in life is
learning how to deal with it.

Get busy living 
or
 get busy dying.

Don’t cry 
because it’s over.
Smile
 because it happened.

Life is either 
a daring adventure or nothing at all.
Keep calm and carry on.

Love all
trust a few
do wrong to none.

Life is ours to be spent
 not to be saved.

The greatest pleasure
 of life is love.

Life can be simple and beautiful.
Focus on the good things.

Life is a long lesson 
in humility.

It’s better to dance
 than to march
 through life.

We are who 
we choose to be.

The only impossible journey
 is the one you never begin.
Your best life will not be found in comfort.

Doing is a quantum leap
 from imagining.
Be so good they can’t ignore you.

If you don’t like something
 change it.

All our dreams can come true 
if we have the courage
 to pursue them.

The dreamers are the saviors
 of the world.

Life is to entered
 upon with courage.
Life is a single player game.

Life is the art
of drawing sufficient conclusions
from insufficient premises.

Life is a process.
We are a process.
The universe is a process.

Life is beautiful
because it doesn’t last.

Reverence for life
is the highest court of appeal.

The tragedy of life
is what dies inside a man
while he lives.

Life is wide, limitless.
There is no border, no frontier.

Life is about learning.
When you stop learning,
you die.

Life is not an exact science
it is an art.

Love is a better teacher
than duty.

Life is a series
 of baby steps.

Love yourself first
and everything else 
falls into line.

Don't give it five minutes
if you're not going to
 give it five years.

I've failed over and over
and that is why I succeed.

Nothing can dim the light 
that shines from within.

Sometimes you will never know
 the value of a moment
 until it becomes a memory.

Only I can change my life.
No one can do it for me.

If everything was perfect
you would never learn
and you would never grow.

Life is like riding a bicycle.
To keep your balance
you must keep moving.

Life isn't about finding yourself.
Life is about creating yourself.

It is not the length of life
but depth of life.

Where there is no struggle
there is no strength.

Above all
be the heroine of your life
not the victim.

It's not whether you get knocked down.
It's whether you get up.

Remember
no one can make you feel inferior
 without your consent.

Yesterday is not ours to recover
but tomorrow is ours to win or lose.

Knowing what must be done
 does away with fear.

Your time is limited
so don't waste it
living someone else's life.

Innovation distinguishes 
between a leader and a follower.

I want to put a ding
in the universe.

Sometimes life is going to hit you 
in the head with a brick.
Don't lose faith.

Things don't have to change the world
 to be important.

I'm as proud of
 what we don't do
as I am of what we do.

Life is not fair;
get used to it.

Your most unhappy customers
are your greatest source of learning.

If you can't make it good
at least make it look good.

If you think your teacher is tough
wait until you get a boss.
He doesn't have tenure.

It's fine to celebrate success
but it is more important
to heed the lessons of failure.

Success is a lousy teacher.
It seduces smart people
into thinking they can't lose.

I could either watch it happen
 or be a part of it.

The first step is to establish that something is possible;
then probability will occur.

Failure is an option here.
If things are not failing
you are not innovating enough.

Persistence is very important.
You should not give up
unless you are forced to give up.

When something is important enough
you do it
even if the odds are not in your favor.

Price is what you pay.
Value is what you get.

Risk comes from
not knowing what you're doing.

I always knew
I was going to be rich.
I don't think I ever doubted it for a minute.

After all
you only find out who is swimming naked
when the tide goes out.

Whatever you are
be a good one.

My Best Friend is a person
who will give me a book
I have not read.

I am a slow walker
but I never walk back.

The best way to predict your future
 is to create it.

I laugh because I must not cry
 that is all.

I will prepare
and some day
 my chance will come.

Every man's happiness
 is his own responsibility.
Achievement has no color.

I do the very best I know how
the very best I can
and I mean to keep on doing so until the end.

Get books
sit yourself down anywhere
and go to reading them yourself.

Success is not final
Failure is not fatal
It is the courage to continue that counts.

Never give in
never give in
never
never
never
never.

Some people want it to happen
some wish it would happen
others make it happen.

Talent wins games
but teamwork and intelligence wins championships.

I can accept failure
but I can't accept not trying.

Always turn a negative situation
into a positive situation.

You must expect great things of yourself
 before you can do them.

If you quit ONCE
it becomes a habit.
Never quit.

Everybody has talent
but ability takes hard work.

Never say never
because limits, like fears
are often just an illusion.

To learn to succeed
you must first learn to fail.
Make It Happen.

If you do the work you get rewarded.
There are no shortcuts in life.
The key to success is failure.
Always deliver more than expected.

Every time we launch a feature
people yell at us.

Make every detail perfect
and limit the number of details to perfect.

Always look for the fool in the deal.
If you don’t find one,
it’s you.
Chase the vision, not the money, the money will end up following you.

Nothing works better 
than just improving your product.

Get big quietly
so you don’t tip off
potential competitors.

It's kind of fun
 to do the impossible.

The way to get started
is to quit talking
and begin doing.

All our dreams can come true
if we have the courage to pursue them.
Even miracles take a little time.

The flower that blooms in adversity
is the most rare and beautiful of all.
Don't just fly, soar

Believe you can
then you will.
Today is a good day to try.

Listen with your heart
you will understand.
Giving up is for rookies.

Always 
let your conscience 
be your guide.
Change is good.

The only thing predictable
 about life is
its unpredictability.

Remember
you're the one
who can fill the world with sunshine.
Data beats emotions.

I never dreamed about success,
I worked for it.

See things in the present
even if they are in the future.

Life’s a journey.
It’s a journey about discovering limits.

You have to act
and
act now.

Diligence is the mother
of good luck.

He that falls in love with himself
will have no rivals.

Well done is better
than well said.
No gains without pains.

Lost Time is
never found again.
Haste makes Waste.

Search others for their virtues
thy self for thy vices.

Act
as if what you do makes a difference.
It does.
Believe you can and you're halfway there.

Limit your 'always'
 and your 'nevers.'

Try to be a rainbow 
in someone else's cloud.

You do not find the happy life.
You make it.

It isn't where you came from.
It's where you're going that counts.
You get what you give.

Happiness is not by chance
but by choice.

If I can't do great things
I can do small things in a great way.

Don't wait.
The time will never be just right.

Keep your face always toward the sunshine
and shadows will fall behind you.

As long as we persevere and endure
we can get anything we want.

I love to hit people
I love to.

If you can concentrate always on the present
you'll be a happy man.

A wise man
will make more opportunities
 than he finds.
Kites rise highest against the wind.
Luck is the residue of design.

It's choice
- not chance - 
that determines your destiny.
It ain't over till it's over.

It's like déjà vu
all over again.
A nickel ain't worth a dime anymore.

If you don't know where you are going
you'll end up someplace else.

Without haste
but without rest.

Nothing is worth
more than this day.

As soon as you trust yourself
you will know how to live.

Doubt can only be removed
by action.

Knowing is not enough.
we must apply.
Willing is not enough.
we must do.

Keep your face to the sunshine
and you cannot see the shadows.

Although the world is full of suffering,
it is also full of the overcoming of it.

The only thing worse than being blind
is having sight but no vision.
Slow and steady wins the race.

The gods help them
that help themselves.

To find yourself
think for yourself.

I know nothing
except the fact of my ignorance.

One thing only I know
and that is that I know nothing.

Choose to be optimistic
it feels better.

Be happy
but never satisfied.
Achievement is talent plus preparation.

Hard work is a prison sentence
only if it does not have meaning.

Working really hard
is what successful people do.

I have not failed.
I've just found 10,000 ways
that won't work.

It is never too late
to be what you might have been.
Everything you can imagine is real.

Life isn't about finding yourself.
Life is about creating yourself.

Always do
what you are afraid to do.
Turn your wounds into wisdom.

You never fail
until you stop trying.

Do not fear failure
but rather fear not trying.

Never lose hope.
Storms make people stronger and never last forever.

Be brave
to stand for what you believe in
even if you stand alone.

The man who moves a mountain
begins by carrying away small stones.
Rejection is an opportunity for your selection.

Don't spend time beating on a wall
hoping to transform it into a door.

Doubt kills more dreams
than failure ever will.

Life always begins with one step
outside of your comfort zone.

A quitter never wins
and a winner never quits.

I do not like to repeat successes
I like to go on to other things.

People are successful
because they think and act like successful people.

The secret to success
is constancy of purpose.

The power to change your life
lies in the simplest of steps.
Excuse Me While I Succeed!
